 cổ điển thất truyền, lấy tri thức xưa làm đuốc, từng bước dò đường giữa bóng tối. Giữa chiến địa phong kín, hắn gặp lại người con gái mang dung nhan phượng hoàng dưới lớp ngụy trang. Hai người kề vai trong máu lửa, lấy sinh tử vá lại niềm tin, đập tan mưu đồ hắc ám.</p>","tmdb_id":282158,"cast":["Xinran Yang","Đoàn Nghi Hiên","Sanshi","童思琦","乔耀辉","李乘风","葉保華","Liu Mingyue","Li Lanling","Zheng Liu","Zhenyan Liu","Lin Maomao","Tong Yin","Yeqiao Yan","孙佳禾"],"director":["Yuanjun Zeng"],"keywords":[],"tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"282158","season":1,"vote_average":8,"vote_count":1},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Xinran Yang","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Xinran Yang","tmdb_id":5318606,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hYd3sl7KlVFKyqOiTpFaiHj7OpD.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/5318606"},{"name":"Đoàn Nghi Hiên","name_vi":"Đoàn Nghi Hiên","name_original":"Duan Yixuan","tmdb_id":2206686,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t0SFESlym4mWsrhNM3V1qY7ZQXo.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2206686"},{"name":"Sanshi","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Sanshi","tmdb_id":4316658,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ajQVjnlrTOw6M8qSrwjBXlcCFkg.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4316658"},{"name":"童思琦","name_vi":null,"name_original":"童思琦","tmdb_id":5975179,"profile":null,"tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/5975179"},{"name":"乔耀辉","name_vi":null,"name_original":"乔耀辉","tmdb_id":5975180,"profile":null,"tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/5975180"},{"name":"李乘风","name_vi":null,"name_original":"李乘风","tmdb_id":5975181,"profile":null,"tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/5975181"},{"name":"葉保華","name_vi":null,"name_original":"葉保華","tmdb_id":5327212,"profile":null,"tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/5327212"},{"name":"Liu Mingyue","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Liu Mingyue","tmdb_id":2156556,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kqh1vBsQ35b617dvd9jtvQ2ii7l.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themovi